ordinario: confianza, valores, empatía y una cultura sólida. También exploramos la historia de su reconocida empresa “Biomédica de Referencia”, ejemplo de excelencia y humanidad. - Un episodio inspirador que revela cómo la cultura organizacional no es un lujo, sino el corazón mismo del éxito." type="episode" contentRating="M/12" duration="3785000" grandparentArt="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/azt/video/thumbnails/widescreen/3840x2160/led_lifestyle.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/69f93b2beb8cee7cdf9ad697" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/69f93b2beb8cee7cdf9ad697" grandparentRatingKey="69f93b2beb8cee7cdf9ad697" grandparentThumb="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/azt/show/thumbnails/widescreen/2000x2858/led_lifestyle.jpg" grandparentTitle="La Entrevista de 24 Lifestyle" grandparentType="show" index="1" originallyAvailableAt="2025-10-17T00:00:00Z" parentIndex="4" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/azt/video/thumbnails/widescreen/3840x2160/led_lifestyle.jpg" title="La Entrevista de 24 Lifestyle" userState="0" year="2025"><Image alt="La Entrevista de 24 Lifestyle" type="coverArt" url="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/azt/video/thumbnails/widescreen/3840x2160/led_lifestyle.jpg"/><Image alt="La Entrevista de 24 Lifestyle" type="coverPoster" url="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/azt/show/thumbnails/widescreen/2000x2858/led_lifestyle.jpg"/><Image alt="La Entrevista de 24 Lifestyle" type="snapshot" url="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/azt/video/thumbnails/widescreen/3840x2160/led_lifestyle.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6171e01d4c451f5a44debdf6" id="6171e01d4c451f5a44debdf6" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6171e01d4c451f5a44debdf6" ratingKey="genre_6171e01d4c451f5a44debdf6" slug="en-espanol" tag="En Espańol" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1778205251" duration="3785000" endsAt="1778209036" id="69f93b38eb8cee7cdf9ad724" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video><Video 